Package com.ibm.team.interop.common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IExternalProxy
    Class to represent a proxy for an external object that is being replicated in the Jazz repository, and possibly synchronized with a Jazz item.
    IExternalProxyHandle
    Represents a handle to an Item proxy.
    IExternalRepositoryConnection
    Represents a connection to an external repository.
    IExternalRepositoryConnectionHandle
    Comment for IExternalRepositoryConnectionHandle
    IExternalState
    Class to represent the replicated state associated with a proxy for an external object.
    IExternalStateHandle
    A handle for an IExternalState item.
    IPropertyMapping
    Class to represent the identification of a property of an external object that is being replicated in a Jazz repository, and possibly synchronized with a property of a Jazz item.
    ISyncRule
    A synchronization rule defines how external object properties and Jazz item properties are transformed into each other.
    ISyncRuleHandle
    Handle for an ISyncRule item.
    IValueMapping
    Class to represent an enumerated value mapping for a synchronized property.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InteropFactory
    Factory class for creating various Interop component objects in memory.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IExternalProxy.SynchronizationDirection
    Possible values for the LAST_SYNC_DIRECTION property.
    IExternalProxy.SynchronizationStatus
    Possible values for the SYNC_STATUS_PROPERTY.
